Dorothy Coburn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dorothy_Coburn 0 Dorothy Coburn (June 8, 1905 – May 15, 1978) was an American film actress who appeared in a number of early Laurel and Hardy silents. She was a niece of author Walt Coburn, and granddaughter of Robert Coburn Sr., founder of the Circle C Ranch in Montana.
